yb: a dynamic mdbook focus on searching functionality

dependencies:
1. install pandoc and add it into environments
```
# on windows
scoop install pandoc
# on Ubuntu
sudo apt update && sudo apt install pandoc
```

flags:
-h: print help message
-s: start server
-n: create a new blog structure in current directory
-v: print version

Usage:
yb -h
yb -s
yb -n
yb -v

quick start:
```sh
yb -n
yb -s
```
then visit http://localhost:8080/blog/